    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >森林裡到處都是易怒、討厭的駝鹿，讓自己沉浸在一個可以解謎的輕鬆的冒險世界中吧！你扮演一個迷路的伐木工人，經常面臨憤怒的駝鹿的衝击和一般的“惡作劇”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287140/extras/725764c73b91ffe6e8c133cdd5bec35f.poster.avif?t=1732724534\" width=752 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287140/extras/725764c73b91ffe6e8c133cdd5bec35f.webm?t=1732724534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287140/extras/725764c73b91ffe6e8c133cdd5bec35f.mp4?t=1732724534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在現實生活中，你只需移動駝鹿過路標誌，就可以讓駝鹿離開你，但這裡不一樣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必須避開駝鹿（米斯? ），激怒它們，讓它們沖向你想要它們去的地方。您順便讓它們沖向其它駝鹿，看看會發生什麼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287140/extras/f9a7355f19f6cd1dcdf81d0d52b69396.poster.avif?t=1732724534\" width=752 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287140/extras/f9a7355f19f6cd1dcdf81d0d52b69396.webm?t=1732724534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287140/extras/f9a7355f19f6cd1dcdf81d0d52b69396.mp4?t=1732724534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以躲在樹後面，推著駝鹿前面的木塊偷偷溜過去。你甚至可以把駝鹿裝上軌道車，推著它們走。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287140/extras/cd52e1b81f25a19410a62e78692d806c.poster.avif?t=1732724534\" width=800 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287140/extras/cd52e1b81f25a19410a62e78692d806c.webm?t=1732724534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287140/extras/cd52e1b81f25a19410a62e78692d806c.mp4?t=1732724534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無論你做什麼，不要被踐踏。駝鹿不是小氣的動物。它們就是不喜歡你。Mooselutions是一款回合制的Sokoban風格的遊戲，所以你在激怒駝鹿後有一個回合的時間逃離它們。不要跑到憤怒的駝鹿的路上!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這裡有49道手工製作的駝鹿謎題，用來測試你的技能，隨著遊戲的推進，不同的區域會解鎖。你可以隨心所欲地操纵驼鹿，讓它们讨厌你，從而获得成就。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >誰會想到這麼簡單的與駝鹿有關的規則會帶來這麼多深奧的駝鹿謎題？這就是駝鹿所說的心理糾纏。</p>",
